  "description": "<p> Where your drive fuels your success! 🌟<br />📍 Office located @ Raffles / Boat Quay📈 Career progression opportunities <br />🥊 Training provided </p><p><em><strong>Looking out for:</strong></em></p><ul><li>Fresh grad/ORD & Career switch</li><li>Leadership & guidance 📚</li><li>Flexible schedule 📆</li><li>Personal development 🧑‍🎓</li><li>Work well independently and in team environment 🤜🏽🤛🏽</li><li>Overseas training & trips ✈️ (Malaysia, Taiwan, Hong Kong, Indonesia)</li><li>Responsibilities for this role:</li><li>Conduct face-to-face sales presentation 📊</li><li>Provide great customer service 🔊</li><li>Able to adapt rapid changes 💱</li></ul><p><strong>Singaporean and PR only. </strong></p><p>💪 Work hard, earn big, and enjoy the ride! Your incredible journey starts here.</p>",
